cs.LO, cs.AR, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.DC 

The paper deals with formal verification of micro-architectural models, which involves logic and reasoning. Hence, cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with formal semantics, which falls under cs.AR (Architecture), and formal languages, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages). The paper also deals with the correctness and performance of multi-core processors, which falls under cs.SE (Software Engineering), and communication fabrics, which falls under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
